 done.  I'd like to work on the following steps, some of which appear to be mainly for faction.  If I do not have enough faction, some of the NPCs needed for the quest will not spawn.<br><br>1)  Test of Patience - Go to Eurid's Crossing and find Ooglyn (-900, +1600).  Then go in the water (-1600, +4200) to talk to Abe the Abandoned.  Then talk to a Greater Spirit.  While we are in the ocean, apparently there will be sharks to hunt while we wait.<br><br>2)  Test of Wisdom - Head to West Karana to find a Wandering Spirit.  Then go to Rathe Mountains to find <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=5238">Tabien the Goodly</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> and kill him.  Then kill <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=5183">Glaron the Wicked</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->.  Go back to the Wandering Spirit to get a NO RENT gem.  Take this to Emerald Jungle and get the reward:  <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=1123">Shield of Falsehood</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br><br>I have already got the component for the second reward:  <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=1784">Black Fur Boots</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> but I need to hitch a ride to Emerald Jungle (and have some protection) to get my booties.<br><br>The remainder of the quest is probably beyond my reach at this point but results in <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=748">The Spear of Fate</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   If you are interested in joining this quest, please post your name, class, level and guild.<br><br>The chat channel will be shammy:tears</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  EDIT:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Please also note that I <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  may</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> try the Test of Patience on my own using Invisibility to Animals before Thursday (I'm impatient, what can I say?).  If I succeed, that leaves only the Test of Wisdom, and we would almost certainly have time to do a leg of someone else's epic that wants to get started.  Please send me an email if you would like to start your epic this Thursday or within the next few weeks. If possible, please detail the steps you need to complete and a link to your epic's description. tigonie@hotmail.com <p>Talcee<br>Shaman of the 35th Season<br>An Elder of <a href=http://www.webhazard.net>The Tears of Veeshan</a><br>(a.k.a. Tigonie Silvanstar)<br>It's Tal-see, not Talc-ie.  It you persist in calling her Talc-ie, I'll name her Talcee Footwear!  ;)</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/utalcee.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Talcee</A> at: 5/18/02 6:05:52 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/usolarianne.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Solarianne</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>ToV Guild Leader</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/18/02 8:46:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/ftearsofveeshan25764frm14.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=55.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Epic Thursday - May 23</span><hr size=1> Early start for me, but I'll be around later on if you need help.<br>~7pm PST. <p><B><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=117690">Solarianne Starforge</A></B><BR>High Priestess of Tunare<BR>Leader, <A HREF="http://www.webhazard.net">Tears of Veeshan</A><BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/ucranceclearspirit.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Crance Clearspirit</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/19/02 7:35:06 am)</font><br>